    • get

      public SpiritPermissions.ChangePermissions get(net.minecraft.world.entity.player.Player player)
      Return the permissions for the given player. Returns SpiritPermissions.ChangePermissions.INHERIT_DEFAULT if this player has no permissions registered.
      Parameters:
      player - The player to check.
      Returns:
